    </div>
  </div></section>
  <section class="bg-red-brand text-white py-4"><div class="section text-center"><p class="text-sm font-medium">⚠️ Don't wait for a violation. NYC Fire Code violations carry escalating daily fines and FDNY vacate orders. FDNY is one of the world's most active fire code enforcement agencies.</p></div></section>
  <section class="py-16"><div class="section">
    <div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">Fire Protection Services for New York Businesses</h2><p class="text-base text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We provide every fire safety service your New York commercial property needs to stay compliant with Fire Department of New York (FDNY) requirements and NFPA standards.</p></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card p-6 flex flex-col"><div class="text-3xl mb-3">🧯</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Fire Extinguisher Inspection &amp; Service</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-3">NFPA 10 compliant fire extinguisher inspections for New York commercial properties. Monthly visual checks, annual professional inspections, 6-year internal examinations, and 12-year hydrostatic testing. All service by licensed fire protection technicians.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand bg-red-light px-2 py-1 rounded">NFPA 10</span><button onclick={`openRFQ('','','Fire Extinguisher Service - ${city}, ${state}')`} class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand hover:underline bg-transparent border-0 cursor-pointer">Get Quote →</button></div></div>
      <div class="card p-6 flex flex-col"><div class="text-3xl mb-3">🔔</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Fire Alarm System Installation &amp; Testing</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-3">Complete fire alarm system design, installation, and annual testing for New York commercial buildings. Addressable and conventional systems, smoke detectors, pull stations, horn/strobes, and monitoring. Full compliance with NFPA 72 and Fire Department of New York (FDNY) requirements.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand bg-red-light px-2 py-1 rounded">NFPA 72</span><button onclick={`openRFQ('','','Fire Alarm Installation - ${city}, ${state}')`} class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand hover:underline bg-transparent border-0 cursor-pointer">Get Quote →</button></div></div>
      <div class="card p-6 flex flex-col"><div class="text-3xl mb-3">💧</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Fire Sprinkler System Installation &amp; Inspection</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-3">Fire sprinkler design, installation, and inspection for New York commercial properties. Wet, dry, pre-action, and deluge systems. Quarterly, semi-annual, and five-year inspections per NFPA 25. NYC enforces its own local Fire Code — not the IFC or NY State Code. All fire protection work requires NYC-specific contractor licenses separate from state licensing.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand bg-red-light px-2 py-1 rounded">NFPA 13 / NFPA 25</span><button onclick={`openRFQ('','','Fire Sprinkler Inspection - ${city}, ${state}')`} class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand hover:underline bg-transparent border-0 cursor-pointer">Get Quote →</button></div></div>
      <div class="card p-6 flex flex-col"><div class="text-3xl mb-3">🍳</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Commercial Kitchen Fire Suppression</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-3">Wet chemical fire suppression for New York restaurants and food service operations. Design, installation, semi-annual inspection, and recharge. Ansul, Amerex, and Kidde certified. Required for all commercial cooking per NFPA 96.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand bg-red-light px-2 py-1 rounded">NFPA 96</span><button onclick={`openRFQ('','','Kitchen Suppression - ${city}, ${state}')`} class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand hover:underline bg-transparent border-0 cursor-pointer">Get Quote →</button></div></div>
      <div class="card p-6 flex flex-col"><div class="text-3xl mb-3">📋</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Fire Code Compliance Consulting</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-3">Fire code compliance audits, violation remediation, and pre-inspection consulting for New York commercial properties. We help property managers resolve Fire Department of New York (FDNY) violations and prepare for inspections under the NYC Fire Code.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand bg-red-light px-2 py-1 rounded">NFPA 101</span><button onclick={`openRFQ('','','Fire Code Compliance - ${city}, ${state}')`} class="text-xs font-bold text-red-brand hover:underline bg-transparent border-0 cursor-pointer">Get Quote →</button></div></div>
    </div>
